    1:   #is the simple instruction where any person who have the accsess can get notification on what home is happen
Mobile App Integration Configuration (For both Android and iOS):
In your Home Assistant configuration.yaml file, enable the mobile app integration. This should look something like:
        #simple example of code
mobile_app:
    2:#Device Tracking Configuration:
Next, set up device tracking for your phone to track its location. Here's an example using the device_tracker component in your configuration.yaml:
    #simple code
  device_tracker:
  - platform: mobile_app
    consider_home: 180
    track_new_devices: yes
